<use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 03, 2025</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104wyt1665702609153.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/wyt1665702609153.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/wyt1665702609153.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"wyt1665702609153\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Label </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">A Label is a Development Object that contains text that appears on a presentation\n      component. Labels have properties, but most cannot be set dynamically. </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wyt1665702609153__section_w191ab1b5b1_w192ab1b5_w193ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\"></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wyt1665702609153__section_w194ab1b5b3_w195ab1b5_w196ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d757172e56\"> Characteristics </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"wyt1665702609153__table_d10622e1_d10623e1_d10624e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"wyt1665702609153__table_d10622e1_d10623e1_d10624e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Characteristics</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"wyt1665702609153__table_d10622e1_d10623e1_d10624e1__entry__2\"></th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wyt1665702609153__table_d10622e1_d10623e1_d10624e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Icon:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wyt1665702609153__table_d10622e1_d10623e1_d10624e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\"><img alt=\"Icon\" class=\"image\" id=\"wyt1665702609153__image_e4m_nq4_mwb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/label.png?_LANG=enus\"/></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wyt1665702609153__table_d10622e1_d10623e1_d10624e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Object type code:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wyt1665702609153__table_d10622e1_d10623e1_d10624e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">lbl</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wyt1665702609153__table_d10622e1_d10623e1_d10624e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Main Development Object?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wyt1665702609153__table_d10622e1_d10623e1_d10624e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">No</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wyt1665702609153__table_d10622e1_d10623e1_d10624e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Part of:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wyt1665702609153__table_d10622e1_d10623e1_d10624e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ifc1665702608950.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ifc1665702608950.html\" title=\"A Component is a Main Development Object that defines an executable part of an application. It defines the data structure used to access data, the layout (if applicable) used to present it, and the actions used to modify, validate, and store data.\">Component</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yth1665702550544.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yth1665702550544.html\" title=\"A Component Entity is a Development Object that represents data that is owned by a Component. It is part of the Component’s structure and is maintained as part of the Component, although it may reference and inherit from a Modeled Entity.\">Component Entity</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wyt1665702609153__table_d10622e1_d10623e1_d10624e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Contains:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wyt1665702609153__table_d10622e1_d10623e1_d10624e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jgi1665702550212.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jgi1665702550212.html\" title=\"A Property is a named, typed attribute of Development Object that defines a characteristic or behavior of the object. Each property has a descriptive name, a literal name, a data type, and a value. If no value is specified, a default value may be used.\">Property</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wyt1665702609153__table_d10622e1_d10623e1_d10624e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Generalization:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wyt1665702609153__table_d10622e1_d10623e1_d10624e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ulo1665702550460.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ulo1665702550460.html\" title=\"A Uniface Development Object is an abstract data type that defines the characteristics and behavior of a logical application unit, such as a Component, Field, Message, Library, and so on.\">Development Object</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wyt1665702609153__table_d10622e1_d10623e1_d10624e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Specializations:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wyt1665702609153__table_d10622e1_d10623e1_d10624e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"idk1665702609240.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/idk1665702609240.html\" title=\"An Associated Label belongs to a Component Field. The text of an associated label can be changed using ProcScript.\">Associated Label</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dxr1665702609315.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dxr1665702609315.html\" title=\"A non-associated label is a Label that contains static text that is not associated with a Component Field. It cannot be directly addressed in ProcScript.\">Non-Associated Label</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wyt1665702609153__table_d10622e1_d10623e1_d10624e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Compilation Output:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wyt1665702609153__table_d10622e1_d10623e1_d10624e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wyt1665702609153__table_d10622e1_d10623e1_d10624e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">URI format:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wyt1665702609153__table_d10622e1_d10623e1_d10624e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">lbl:<var class=\"keyword varname\">FieldName</var>\n</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">lbl:<var class=\"keyword varname\">LabelName</var>\n</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wyt1665702609153__section_w197ab1b5b5_w198ab1b5_w199ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d757172e286\"> Specialization </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wyt1665702609153__p_d95714e1_d95715e1_d95716e1\">Label specializes Development Object in the following\n            ways:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wyt1665702609153__li_d38549e1_d38550e1_d38551e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wyt1665702609153__p_d95717e1_d95718e1_d95719e1\">Its has a component or component entity as\n                  parent object.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wyt1665702609153__li_d38552e1_d38553e1_d38554e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wyt1665702609153__p_d95720e1_d95721e1_d95722e1\">It has no child development objects or code\n                  containers.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wyt1665702609153__section_w200ab1b5b7_w201ab1b5_w202ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d757172e310\"> Properties </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wyt1665702609153__p_d95726e1_d95727e1_d95728e1\">Object Properties:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wyt1665702609153__li_d38555e1_d38556e1_d38557e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jrq1665702585385.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jrq1665702585385.html\" title=\"Name of the development object, which uniquely identifies it.\">Name</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wyt1665702609153__li_d38558e1_d38559e1_d38560e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"owq1665702585461.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/owq1665702585461.html\" title=\"Type of Development Object. Read only.\">Type</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wyt1665702609153__li_d38561e1_d38562e1_d38563e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ybn1665702585544.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ybn1665702585544.html\" title=\"Complete URI of the Development Object. Read only.\">Location</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wyt1665702609153__li_d38564e1_d38565e1_d38566e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xrw1665702585620.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xrw1665702585620.html\" title=\"Use this property to briefly describe the development object in up to 256 Unicode characters.\">Description</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wyt1665702609153__li_d38567e1_d38568e1_d38569e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ipc1665702585697.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ipc1665702585697.html\" title=\"Use this property to provide comments or instructions for the selected development object. You can use the toolbar and standard Windows keyboard shortcuts to format the text, copy and paste, and undo and redo edits.\">Documentation</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wyt1665702609153__p_d95729e1_d95730e1_d95731e1\">Configuration Properties:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wyt1665702609153__li_d38570e1_d38571e1_d38572e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jtg1665702585772.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jtg1665702585772.html\" title=\"This property indicates whether the current object inherits from a modeled object. Boolean read-only.\">Inherits</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wyt1665702609153__li_d38573e1_d38574e1_d38575e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"tgz1665702585851.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tgz1665702585851.html\" title=\"This property specifies the name of the development object from which the current object inherits. Depending on the context, it may be read-only or editable.\">Inherits From</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wyt1665702609153__li_d38576e1_d38577e1_d38578e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yjf1665702609397.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yjf1665702609397.html\" title=\"This property specifies the fully qualified name of the associated field.\">Associated Field</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wyt1665702609153__p_d95732e1_d95733e1_d95734e1\">Presentation properties:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wyt1665702609153__li_d38579e1_d38580e1_d38581e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xcr1665702586927.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xcr1665702586927.html\" title=\"Text of the label. If the label is attached to a field, it can be set in ProcScript using the $labelproperties function.\">Label Text</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wyt1665702609153__p_d95735e1_d95736e1_d95737e1\">Presentation properties in forms and reports:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wyt1665702609153__li_d38582e1_d38583e1_d38584e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mpr1665702587008.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mpr1665702587008.html\" title=\"Position of an object frame on a horizontal axis relative to its parent, excluding the border (if present); expressed as number of character cells.\">Left (xpos)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wyt1665702609153__li_d38585e1_d38586e1_d38587e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"aon1665702587081.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aon1665702587081.html\" title=\"Position of an object frame on a vertical axis relative to its parent, excluding the border (if present); expressed as number of character cells.\">Top (ypos)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wyt1665702609153__li_d38588e1_d38589e1_d38590e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"swp1665702587155.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/swp1665702587155.html\" title=\"Width of the object frame in the layout of a Form or Report, expressed in character cells, excluding the border (if present).\">Width (xsize)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wyt1665702609153__li_d38591e1_d38592e1_d38593e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"nai1665703058765.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nai1665703058765.html\" title=\"Height of the object frame in the layout of a Form or Report, expressed in character cells, excluding the border (if present).\">Height (ysize)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wyt1665702609153__li_d38594e1_d38595e1_d38596e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"thz1665702609551.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/thz1665702609551.html\" title=\"Font to use for the label, and for tool tip text for widgets (if they support tool tips). The listed fonts are determines by the application's .ini file.\">Label Font</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wyt1665702609153__li_d38597e1_d38598e1_d38599e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"asq1665702609631.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/asq1665702609631.html\" title=\"Horizontal alignment of the label—Left, Right, or Center.\">Horizontal Alignment</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wyt1665702609153__li_d38600e1_d38601e1_d38602e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rjx1665702609708.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rjx1665702609708.html\" title=\"Vertical alignment of the label— Top(default), Bottom, or Center.\">Vertical Alignment</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wyt1665702609153__li_d38603e1_d38604e1_d38605e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"kvj1665702609788.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kvj1665702609788.html\" title=\"Determines whether the widget is transparent.\">Transparency</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wyt1665702609153__li_d38606e1_d38607e1_d38608e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wwg1665702587409.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wwg1665702587409.html\" title=\"Code that identifies a Uniface index color, which represents a combination of background and foreground colors. Applicable only to Form components. Deprecated.\">Index Color</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wyt1665702609153__li_d38609e1_d38610e1_d38611e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jwc1665702609865.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jwc1665702609865.html\" title=\"Determines whether the label is repeated when multiple occurrences are drawn. Valid values are Do no repeat (default), Repeat if not empty, or Repeat.\">Repetition</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wyt1665702609153__li_d38612e1_d38613e1_d38614e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fcv1665702609942.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fcv1665702609942.html\" title=\"Determines whether the background and foreground colors of the parent entity or form can be inherited. This property can be set in ProcScript for the widgets, but not for labels. Valid Values are True or False (default).\">Inherit Colors (InheritColors)</a> (<span class=\"ph filepath\">.ini</span> file only) </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wyt1665702609153__li_d38615e1_d38616e1_d38617e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"kyj1665702610018.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kyj1665702610018.html\" title=\"Determines whether a label moves with its associated field when the field is repositioned.\">Anchor</a>(<span class=\"ph filepath\">.ini</span> file only) </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gya1665702610097.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Frame</a><p>A Frame is a Development Object that graphically represents a Development Object in the layout of a Form or Report component.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3616850\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3616850\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Label Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 03, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Label A Label is a Development Object that contains text that appears on a presentation component. Labels have properties, but most cannot be set dynamically. Characteristics Characteristics Icon: Object type code: lbl Main Development Object? No Part of: Component , Component Entity Contains: Property Generalization: Development Object Specializations: Associated Label , Non-Associated Label Compilation Output: — URI format: lbl: FieldName | lbl: LabelName Specialization Label specializes Development Object in the following ways: Its has a component or component entity as parent object. It has no child development objects or code containers. Properties Object Properties: Name Type Location Description Documentation Configuration Properties: Inherits Inherits From Associated Field Presentation properties: Label Text Presentation properties in forms and reports: Left (xpos) Top (ypos) Width (xsize) Height (ysize) Label Font Horizontal Alignment Vertical Alignment Transparency Index Color Repetition Inherit Colors (InheritColors) ( .ini file only) Anchor ( .ini file only) Related Links Frame A Frame is a Development Object that graphically represents a Development Object in the layout of a Form or Report component. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}